Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What do you think we saved that little kid for, second lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Are you trying to be\N"Paladin, the Man of the West" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just thinking about doing her too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's fine. As long as you wait for your turn—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a good-for-nothing rogue who's no better than a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you lay a finger on this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Larkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Quebec.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sierra Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morales has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morales is moving into the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Quebec, this is Lima Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has moved to Phase 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa Ana has taken a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morales and Sesma as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Quebec to each observer section.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the CP and move to the ORP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hotel Quebec Actual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin, Golf One.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Davy Crockett to the Lone Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: Get Davy Crockett to the Lone Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Code confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's begin to withdraw... perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Dear God, our deeply loving father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father never did anything bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In his every word and deed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he had nothing to be ashamed of before God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet God...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blame not the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kills a man is always...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that human thinking? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know the answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know it too well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so well that I do not have the words to convey it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Rosarita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave here as soon as the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a friend's daughter comes over for a visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be dishonored to let her leave without showing any hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would not be so bad to settle down for a minute and think together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about where to go next, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rolling around the mountain and\Nrunning away can come afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Señor Diego...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please excuse my dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day was so beautiful,\NI thought of tending the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You could leave it to the gardener.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody works here. Not for a mansion this old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Señor, where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Please be my guest and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be uncomfortable if I were to merely freeload.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Borrowing the façade of a maid makes me uneasy already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, please think of me as a genuine servant of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that this is a gun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the first Lovelace set his foot upon the New World with Pizzaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those weapons have remained with the Lovelace family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were good times and bad times,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I look at these weapons\Nin slumber, I realize how
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the motto of our family that was formed amidst the wars now belongs to a distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charity for the saints,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers for the dead;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding a sword for justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sanction of death for the villainous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, please forgive me for not telling you of the abominable cruelty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What were they thinking when they killed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They do not think at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They need not even restrain their emotions or remain calm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no such thing as emotion exists there in the first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They do not care about the ones they killed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are better off killing those people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such is the path that I myself have followed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it cannot be helped even if I were to burn in the fires of Hell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, Master...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and certainly the Young Master should not be responsible for such a sin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Young Master, I believed that night at Roanapur{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}would be the last night I laid my hands on a gun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not gloss over it with excuses of retaliation and such.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a merciless struggle among the filthy canine beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on the name of Santa Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to counter every injustice with an iron hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just let the NSA's attitude slide this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are very clearly stepping into our zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their executive unit was last captured in Manila, for heaven's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they hate our hard-grown little garden that much, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cathy, another cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put a lot of sugar and milk in it, enough for a pancake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will call Dr. Kaufmann!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the challenge is to avoid warfare between the intelligence agencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and figure out what we can obtain\Nby exchanging what, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Now our correspondent on the scene...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tension on the Laos border still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to our relationship with Thai Air Forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,landing the air force in the target's\Nvicinity will not be possible, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're to continue standby, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are trying to step into the CIA's domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's politics, major.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, what is this town called?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Roanapur, major.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such an unpleasant town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we arrived, seven of us almost lost their luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prostitutes gather around in the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the men who purchase them are uniformed policemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much like that town back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of Saigon, South Vietnam in the year 1969—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's that strong smell of corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a Japanese businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's extremely out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all dressed up in a tie in this humid weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really doesn't think much about his safety, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lagoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wallet belongs to one of our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have people looking down on us.\NTeach your apprentice to follow the rules here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here for payment, please wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always require immediate payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave you leeway this time for Colombia Cartel's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't disgrace their reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go talk somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little rowdy inside, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, perfect timing!\NSounds like a match is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. Behind me, a pretty good sniper is aiming at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, please wait until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind giving that much to children on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can never use all our income anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once that happens, the brat will reach for an even fatter purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then your compassion will end up\Nwashing away in a nearby body of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, you really help people out without thinking of the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first amongst those being...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the person in the photo stuck inside this wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say a bullet will never hit the same spot twice,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I just keep it there as a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Are you going for it again, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a person or two:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the skull in the U-boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Romanian twins,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the daughter of that Tokyo yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you've earned disappeared into nothingness for stuff like that, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town is all about nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people end up in their\Ncoffins at Roanapur, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Lagoon Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am just delivering the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief told me to ask. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but he asked me whether we're looking after a strange client.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? It's getting creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's everyone from port merchant Isaac to police chief Watsup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how strange can this person be to\Ncaptivate so many people in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard something interesting just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that dealer of Hotel Moscow, Kowalski?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy said he saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maid, Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who came to reclaim her kidnapped young master
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Venezuela's back country with all the weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That expert terrorist and a goddamn glasses bitch, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one awesome joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Revy, I wouldn't approach the center of things right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be getting in touch with two or three others as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet up at the Yellow Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just learned who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help but sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:15:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I started this business in '78, I've seen fifteen partial and six nearly complete destructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the absolute worst was when that maid-type killing machine appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't start worrying too early or you'll go bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've asked the girls upstairs, but nothing came of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us know if there's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hong Kong Triads are searching for the maid, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if the whole town is beginning to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? There's another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next one is a Colombian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gustavo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the Lagoon pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Señor Abrego?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss is in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HQ said they'll be directly sending us some forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's such a bother when we're not ready for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I sure am blessed by the Virgin Mary today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something to talk about with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the maid, isn't it, Gustavo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've just talked about some forces\Nfrom HQ. I wonder what that's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me the ugly face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's exchange information and we're all happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out. It's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to spill the information. How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you tell me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't actually see that maid last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So first tell me her looks, race, features, and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black hair, a Hispanic but with white skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she dresses like a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's out of her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SPAS in the umbrella, LMG and grenades in the trunk—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's got enough for a whole platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! This is going to be pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. She's out of her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one seemed to be present\Nat the Lagoon Company office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Young Master knew of this place, I have taken the opportunity to greet you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master awaits you at the Sankan Palace Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,related to the Lovelace family?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I work for the Lovelace of South America's thirteen families as a housemaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fabiola Iglesias.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good god, even her speech is just like that goddamn glasses bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While it is but a matter of speech, our chief is not a "glasses bitch."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please revise your statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, is this that maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't, but we are truly in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hint for the quiz came right to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl's pretty heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked up the news articles, it came up right away:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a terrorist bombing in Venezuela's Barinas State last October.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a daily occurrence in South America, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MVR...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the inauguration ceremony of a new party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a party popular among the poor, \Nbut not so welcomed by the capitalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that the head of the\NLovelace family was also on that stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a liberal character atypical of his race.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't understand. Why would that have anything to do with this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl, all the guys here are\Nactually big fans of your chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even we have difficulty locating the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we search together, amigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going to that whatever Hotel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was aware that this town was full of inimical men,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this stench like a horse's stable was indeed that of our family's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready anytime, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stabbed my balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Put your guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is no ordinary maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like that chief maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you pull the guns out as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped to avoid this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidalgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Approach slowly. We don't know what she might be hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's using shotguns!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Revy! You triggered all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't it get interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm making a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's just my guess, but we probably\Nwon't be getting a drink when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and if worse, we might get some holes through our bodies, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then start bombarding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, don't make them shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maid came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marrero, fire it straight into the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that maid! Don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as the chief said. What a town!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends don't care a thing about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab the wounded and get out right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, what a terrible place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up. It's a done deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Chang!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Colombian guys are on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping into the scene now won't help at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more so if the rumor about that maid is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's here to avenge her late master.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's bothering me as much as\Nhaving to pee while I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that the maid's enemy is nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has definitely sneaked into this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which irritates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You win. Is everyone in your\Nhousehold armed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only myself and the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are five maids in the estate including me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the others don't even know that I wield a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was specially selected to ensure the safety of Young Master in the chief's absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sankan Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most expensive hotel in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.47,0:23:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I surely envy him for staying at a suite here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let me introduce again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the twelfth head of the Lovelace of South America's thirteen families,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Garcia Fernando Lovelace's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Lagoon folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, my cute maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola, he said he is only here for a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remain on guard. This town is riddled with filthy humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt, but what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies. Please enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.07,0:24:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are going to smoke, ask him for permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.67,0:24:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Why would I—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.53,0:24:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, would it bother you if I were to light up a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.08,0:24:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no ashtray. Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.76,0:24:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately following the death of my father, a member of a right-wing militia organization was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.01,0:25:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was a terrorist bombing by those not too fond of the rise of a left-wing party.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.37,0:25:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That almost makes too much sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.52,0:25:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes so much sense that it feels contrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.15,0:25:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta held the same suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.44,0:25:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do not have the skills for such an explosion, not to mention they do not need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.50,0:25:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, the police simply closed the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.35,0:25:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, some Air Force officers made a visit to my estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.23,0:25:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MVR, the Fifth Republic Movement—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.07,0:25:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a movement founded by a Venezuelan Air Force officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.86,0:25:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many sympathizers in the Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.18,0:25:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They came to tell us what they had learned over the course of the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.50,0:25:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They re-inspected the staff list for the ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.13,0:25:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looked into the people who went missing after the bombing,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.54,0:25:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and did a check on personal histories of suspicious persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.85,0:25:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it dead on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.46,0:25:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.61,0:25:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of those six were recorded in another document as well:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.42,0:25:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Register of Foreign Intelligence Service of the National Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.53,0:26:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if arranged beforehand, they withdrew from the Service two months prior to the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.60,0:26:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they were all working as stage security officers on the day of the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.03,0:26:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what idiots! They couldn't do worse. They're just worthless brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.57,0:26:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could all just be trimming our nose hair, and that goddamn glasses bitch will defeat them in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.21,0:26:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However... Fabiola.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.27,0:26:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.92,0:26:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.75,0:26:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a photograph we received from the Air Force officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.93,0:26:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was taken in Caracas six months before the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.47,0:26:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was incidentally taken by the military police while investigating another case.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.49,0:26:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man on the right is the leader of the suspicious six, Marcos Jose Lucientes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.67,0:26:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a former major of the Foreign Intelligence Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.72,0:26:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about others?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.67,0:26:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.65,0:26:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day after seeing that picture, Roberta...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.18,0:26:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.61,0:26:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you remember that night at Roanapur?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.19,0:27:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.89,0:27:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sold off like merchandise by a Colombian cartel,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.91,0:27:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you crossed the seas to rescue me,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.97,0:27:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going through all that trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.97,0:27:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.06,0:27:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the late Master was against my involvement to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.53,0:27:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.17,0:27:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. If I was in my father's shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.11,0:27:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have said the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.13,0:27:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.67,0:27:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are all helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.92,0:27:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Roberta...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.13,0:27:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.27,0:27:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Roberta, will always remain by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.82,0:27:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet she disappeared the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.02,0:28:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.12,0:28:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mendes, it's me. Someone's tailing me. Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.82,0:28:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, Mr. Mendes can\Nno longer answer this phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.80,0:28:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.26,0:28:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to know why I have this phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.78,0:28:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Mr. Mendes's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.87,0:28:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that you are the only one who can answer the big question.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.76,0:28:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse of Jose Lucientes was discovered in the canal on the outskirts of Calabozo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.05,0:28:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she figured out his identity and tracked him down, all with a single photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.81,0:29:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder people call her the "Bloodhound."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.07,0:29:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not a bloodhound! She's my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.27,0:29:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Señor Garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.75,0:29:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get back on topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.14,0:29:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.89,0:29:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting back on topic...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.06,0:29:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next person we could trace was the man second from the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.39,0:29:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand who I really am?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.16,0:29:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely. Special Manager of\NStrategic Affairs in South America
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.45,0:29:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the NSA, National Security\NAgency of the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.07,0:29:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the head officer of the Special Program, Colonel Simon Dickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.29,0:29:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am surprised you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.41,0:29:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.09,0:29:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I have heard from Marcos Jose Lucientes,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.83,0:29:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,October's Caracas bombing was planned and carried out by you and your little pet dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.42,0:29:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.08,0:30:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.06,0:30:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are... your dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.39,0:30:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would save me time if you start talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.95,0:30:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while this is still around body temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.19,0:30:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one damn insane woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.95,0:30:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lay a hand on me, the whole U.S. government will become your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.35,0:30:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.21,0:30:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In an abandoned building that was burnt down on\Nthe outskirts of Caracas, Colonel Dickens was found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.22,0:30:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A key witness of this case, a female, purchased a plane ticket from Caracas to Thailand with a stopover in Miami,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.84,0:30:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and, moreover, reserved a long-distance bus ticket from Bangkok to Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.32,0:30:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a U.S. military person on active service. That's for sure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.80,0:30:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.83,0:30:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like where this is going, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.65,0:31:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are you asking us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.07,0:31:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.67,0:31:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, damn it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.90,0:31:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Bao? Closed again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.71,0:31:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Even in this condition,\NI can still serve a drink anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.95,0:31:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you see this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.90,0:31:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here to make fun of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.41,0:31:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,War...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.62,0:31:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chang, I see why you are so cautious today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.32,0:31:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter of money. We're off the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.49,0:31:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.10,0:31:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your chief is going to take on the U.S., an ally of every nation, with her two bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.37,0:32:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please direct me to a store with every item necessary for a war."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.25,0:32:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.75,0:32:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All those who attempted to resist the\Noverwhelming force facing them but couldn't{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.66,0:32:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}head to this town and are led to ruin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.83,0:32:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not requesting this of the Lagoon Company itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.72,0:32:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but personally of you, the Japanese man over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.75,0:32:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.90,0:32:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.80,0:32:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.53,0:32:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please aid in our search for the chief maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.59,0:32:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fully understand that\Nthis is an unreasonable request.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.92,0:32:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.05,0:32:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.18,0:34:04.18,NextEp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,900)\blur10}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.82,0:34:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are the gun, I am the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.36,0:34:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm nothing more than\Na piece of lead right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.55,0:34:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that can light the gunpowder
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.77,0:34:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the gun.
